Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:11.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Fishing for fishies! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:14.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Yahoo!\N--I ain't satisfied, Handa-{\i1}kun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.21,0:00:15.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:19.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,After spending five days of my vacation on this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:22.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...all I did was look for your place...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:26.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...and get a hangover from a bunch of geezers I never met before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:31.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Gimme back my vacation.\N--Serves you right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:35.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're fishin' 'cuz you said you wanted ta enjoy your last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:37.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, middle-schooler...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:41.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What I meant by "enjoy" was that\NI wanted to go on a tour. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:44.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'd know. I dunno anything 'bout tourist spots and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:46.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not satisfied either!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.91,0:00:50.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This was the perfect chance to see Sensei's writing up close!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:52.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we're spending time outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:55.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Guess he wants to be holed up even on a trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:58.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Hiro? You look tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:02.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He was talking to me the whole night about his ideas on calligraphy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:03.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--I started when I was in elementary, and...\N--There's a U23 exhibition, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:07.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--I have a preference as to what brush I use, and...\N--I didn't get a wink of sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:09.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aah...! I want to stay indoors!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.64,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"fake bait hook" "bamboo fishing rod"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.93,0:01:12.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the fishing gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:14.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What can you fish for using this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:16.40,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"bait basket"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.60,0:01:16.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mackerel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.11,0:01:19.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's more to fishing than just putting on bait...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:21.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time I've seen this too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:23.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?! Is this your first time fishing?\N--Wow! A fishing rod!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:24.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:27.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How 'bout you, Kawa-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:30.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lump me in with those city boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:32.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My target: the bass...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:34.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nah... Bass know-how won't help you catch mackerel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:36.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A large blanket can cover a small hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:38.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But it wouldn't keep you from falling in...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:42.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,G-Get it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:46.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Naru?\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:47.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Put some bait in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:49.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:50.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.14,0:01:53.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? There's bait already on the hook...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:54.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Fake bait...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:56.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Come on! Get a hold of it!\N--The rod is so stinky! I don't wanna touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.44,0:01:59.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Too high! Down here!\N--Zip that there mouth of yers an' stay put!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:04.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Speak in Japanese!\N--Sure isn't worth bringing city folks fishing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:05.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm gonna fish up over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:06.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Miwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:09.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?! Hiro-{\i1}nii{\i0}, you ditching me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:12.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a man of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:14.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't goin' for something small-time like mackerel...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:16.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My target...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.66,0:02:18.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}hisanio{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:19.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}hisanio{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:25.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}--Hisanio{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:21.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--The {\i1}hisanio{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:23.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}--Hisanio{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:25.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--That's super, Hiro-{\i1}nii{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:27.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do yer best! I hope ya catch one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The heck is a "{\i1}hisanio{\i0}"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:31.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:33.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's a "miserable fish"? [{\i1}hisan{\i0} = "miserable"; {\i1}o{\i0} = "fish"]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:13.94,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Hisanio"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:13.94,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,76)}"Translation: An expensive fish"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:20.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,First you toss some bait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:26.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Then you drop the line where you tossed the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:28.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,When the tip of the rod bobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:30.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:32.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:34.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma was sayin' that they'd bite good today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:35.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--All right, fishing time!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:37.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have deep-fried mackerel tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:40.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! I think I got something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:41.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it up! Bring it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:42.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:46.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I got two of them...! What a catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Naru?\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:53.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Usually it's the other way around...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Handa! I got three of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:57.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? I can't lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:59.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I got something too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:03.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The pull's so strong! It's got to be big!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:09.04,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Ahahahahahahaha"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:06.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a genius of calligraphy {\i1}and{\i0} fishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:09.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you common rabble that I'm in a league of my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:11.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You caught the shoal...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:14.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Shoal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:25.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta hand it to ya on catchin' the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, wharf roaches!\N--This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:31.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! There's plenty of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:34.53,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"Naru obtained slightly long stick!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:41.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:42.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, gimme your hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:44.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--No!\N--Don't worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:47.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--No...!\N--C'mon, don't worry...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:49.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No...! They bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:58.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I give up...! It stinks, I can't catch any fish, and it's hot! I wanna go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:01.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to go back with all the fish we're catching.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:03.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to write calligraphy with you, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:05.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:09.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like outdoor activities like this either, right, Sensei?! Let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:13.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No way am I going to write calligraphy with you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:15.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you saying such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably just going to say I lost my touch again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:18.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:21.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kosuke! Did you really say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:26.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...it is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:32.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, you gotta see things only your way, eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:35.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're in a slump!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:38.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Slump...? You're not writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not since he saw the work you sent in the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:43.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Handa, you haven't lost your touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:46.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If that was true, you wouldn't be recognized at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:50.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kosuke's been writing with your calligraphy on his mind all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:52.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That must be why he got anxious--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:55.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,he lost his point of reference when you changed your style.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Look at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:00.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:03.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,See how the kids are mimicking her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:06.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Handa, have you ever seen\NKosuke's calligraphy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:09.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No. Why would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:10.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Figured as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:13.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,His calligraphy looks just like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:19.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Handa, yours looks just like your dad's.\NBoth of you are just true to fundamentals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:22.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I got first place with it, so fundamentals should be number one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:25.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You just dissed my old man too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:33.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The role of you young ones is not to fear failure, but to seek new frontiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:34.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Director...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:36.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of setting records, be remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:38.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Lose the match, but win the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:40.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of being number one, aim to be the only one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:43.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of winning awards, strive to make works that sell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:45.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That last one is your desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:47.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Give me... money...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:49.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's being taken away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I learned this from Miwa-{\i1}nee.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:54.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:57.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you tied that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:07:59.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, use Naru's too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:00.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You made one too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:03.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's is super ultra...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:05.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Catch 'em all with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:08.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No way you can fish with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:10.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, is this the "new frontier" you were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:12.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:15.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the epitome of failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:18.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, don't laugh so much. She's only a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:21.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But she's so straightforward and simple...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:28.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Taaackle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:34.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You... brat...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:39.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let ya go with that for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:42.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're having fun down there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:44.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-{\i1}nii{\i0}, you got more bait on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:46.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're out already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:47.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hina spilled 'em all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are Sensei and the others fishing at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:53.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--I found my glasses...!\N--All they've been talking 'bout is calligraphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:55.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Something 'bout losing his touch, or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:58.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you're good, you're good.\NIsn't that all there is to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:01.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If everyone became masters, there'd be nowhere left to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:09.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm probably not gonna catch a {\i1}hisanio{\i0} today either...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:11.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I ain't got a chance this close to land...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:15.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Head Teacher said that he saw someone catch one around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:18.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hiroshi! Did ya catch a {\i1}hisanio{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:21.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single bite. Best we start heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:23.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:26.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What the...? It looks like some cursed tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:28.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:31.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, this'll be my last cast, so I might as well use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:33.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you say "Ebisu."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:38.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Good mojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:43.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They say that if you say "Ebisu" when you cast the line, you'll catch a {\i1}hisanio.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.74,0:09:46.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? "Ebisu"? You mean from the Seven Gods of Fortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:49.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ebisu carries a {\i1}hisanio{\i0} with him, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So a "{\i1}hisanio{\i0}" is a "sea bream"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:53.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,To be specific, I'm fishing for a striped beakfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:56.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you catch them offshore?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:59.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you could catch one here, anyone could become a fisherman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:01.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're so negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:05.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But, if we can catch one, we could have sashimi for dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:06.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ebisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:07.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Serious now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:11.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! There's no way I'm leaving here without eating something good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:22.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No bites...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:23.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:27.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, you're all forgetting we're trying to catch one with {\i1}that{\i0} hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:29.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,All right, time to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:30.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:33.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to clean up, so can you hold this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:34.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:36.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't caught anything anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:38.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:41.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We... We've got a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:01.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:03.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Miwa, the net!\N--Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:05.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Okay, we'll help too!\N--Is it because of Ebisu? Is it because of Ebisu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:07.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?! You're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:10.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You crazy?! No way you can reel in the big one alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:13.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can! I bet you guys are gonna take the credit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:17.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Ebisu! Ebisu!\N--Be quiet over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:18.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:21.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:23.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huge...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:25.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:38.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The heck was that?! That was freaking huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:40.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There actually was one like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:43.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see it drop?! It just plopped back in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:44.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The hook just fell apart in midair!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:07.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we did catch a lot of mackerel, so all's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:08.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deep fry them at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I heard pickling them is good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:19.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:22.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:26.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Since coming to this island, I sometimes get this urge to write calligraphy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:32.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Something rises from inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:34.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...and my hands start to shake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:58.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei caught 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:12:59.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:01.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I'd like to celebrate our visit to the island, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:03.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:04.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:08.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:11.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the fish covered in ink here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:13.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's the remains of the new frontier...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:15.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been better if it was a sea bream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:19.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You guys do your best and get better, and make me rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That sure sounds like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:25.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess we're just products in Kawafuji-{\i1}san{\i0}'s eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:27.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's this 'bout "new frontiers"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:29.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:32.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The other room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:37.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:38.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Snooping around again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:40.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:41.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Lookin' good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:44.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I always liked your writing, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:47.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This one's the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:54.09,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Sea Bream"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:56.59,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Fukue Airport"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:14:01.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuoka flight 635 will start boarding at 10:20...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:05.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, you folks didn't need to come and see us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:08.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a three-hour flight to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:11.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Well, I know you're all sad to see us go,\N--What's this?\N{\i1}--Kankoro mochi{\i0} ["sweet potato rice cakes"].
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:14.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--but you really don't need to worry...\N--It tastes good when ya grill 'em in the toaster oven!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:16.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Kawafuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:19.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's written as "Eight Lightning" to read "Hacchikankan."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:22.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--TV rock's the revolution of rocks!\N--Really, why'd you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:23.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:26.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why are the locals so excited to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:31.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's time before the departure, so you should go and buy some gifts too, Kawafuji-{\i1}kun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:33.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:35.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your generosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:37.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry 'bout it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:40.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei's friends are always welcome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:44.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The kids usually only interact with people nearby,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:47.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,so it looks like they had fun with you city folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:49.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Look at it! Awesome, right?!\N--Hey! They got somethin' here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:51.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all them toys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:54.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The airport's so neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:57.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's like Santa's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:14:58.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna take one with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:04.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what's this island's specialty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:06.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:08.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kankoro mochi{\i0}, camellia candy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:10.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...oval squid... sea urchin...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:12.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...Goto udon... Goto beef...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:14.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can bring that much with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:16.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something besides food?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How about a mobile strap?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:20.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty standard gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:25.42,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"Goto Specialty
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:25.42,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,73)}Baramon-{\i1}kun"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:22.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, not cute at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:25.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's "Baramon-{\i1}kun{\i0}." Buy plenty, and make 'em popular in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:30.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have friends, so I'll just buy one for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:32.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:35.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh... sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:36.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:39.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's gonna buy this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:44.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Buy"? As in you're going to make me buy it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:49.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,For heaven's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:53.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stake your afterlife at your age...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:58.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanna give this to Kawafuji as a gift...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:01.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Darn... I tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know what he'd like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:05.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:08.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You sure bought a lot of gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:11.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I bragged to the guys at work that I was going to Goto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta look good, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:16.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuoka flight 635
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:19.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--will now begin boarding.\N--Oh? It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:21.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Please come to Gate 1 for boarding.\N--Sorry for not doing anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:24.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're not good with stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:29.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was nice seeing you managing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:31.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can put in a good report to Handa-{\i1}sensei{\i0} too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:34.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You've been... seeing my old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:36.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Every so often, for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:39.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He was pretty worried about you, despite being the one who sent you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:44.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:46.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's with that surprised look of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:48.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the way you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:53.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you'd say rebellious stuff like, "He wouldn't worry for me."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:58.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:02.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe my old man doesn't dislike me the way I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.55,0:17:06.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're... just figuring that out now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:08.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Being strict and not liking someone are two separate things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:12.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask an outsider like me, you've got a doting parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:14.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Call him some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:24.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aah...! Did Kawa-{\i1}san{\i0} board already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:27.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet. He's going through now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:32.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's his glasses! His glasses set it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:34.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I knew he'd be caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:36.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You both came here just for this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:38.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not my glasses, my belt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:44.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this is golden! He's sayin' something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:47.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he has a knife rigged into those glasses of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:50.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,As your friend, I'm embarrassed, Kawafuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:52.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:57.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:03.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've been rude this whole time, but...\NI'm happy to have met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:05.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I learned a lot from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:10.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Learned from me? This wasn't a school field trip or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:19.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If we walk the same path,\NI'm sure we'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:22.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And the feeling's mutual.\NI'm happy to have met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:24.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, meeting someone face to face
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:27.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,makes you feel better than being jealous from afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:29.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come again any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:39.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'll come again, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:40.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:49.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this! Are they trying to kill me or what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:52.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Check out the nabbing power of the metal detector!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.39,0:18:55.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I feeling embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:59.30,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"I've done it this time!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:59.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to give 'em the gift that Grandpa told me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:01.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You still have time. Go, Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:02.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:09.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute... She doesn't have any metals on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:19.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Kawa-{\i1}san{\i0} noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:20.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's waving to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:25.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of sad, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:27.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We only just met them, and we're feeling sad already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:29.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:32.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No fair! Gimme some juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:33.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:36.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--He sure can adapt quickly.\N--Gimme...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:39.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo, eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:43.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? You wanna go to Tokyo too, Hiro-{\i1}nii{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:45.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not like I wanna go to Tokyo, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:50.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking that, one day, we're gonna leave the island too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:57.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in my third year of high school, so I gotta start thinking seriously 'bout stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:08.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for ruining my serious scene there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:09.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They're off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:19.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:23.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Bye-bye!\N--Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:26.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:30.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're over the passenger limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:35.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s rental car was returned, so come home by bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:43.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! There's gotta be room for us somewhere!\N--Wait up...! Don't leave us behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:47.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad seeing your friends go, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:49.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:51.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.01,0:22:29.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What was Naru's gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.88,0:22:33.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what was detected...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:34.88,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Naru"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:36.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.92,0:22:38.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.89,0:22:48.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:49.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll come alone.
